data.description: GREAT NEW PRICE on This 4/2.5 Citrus Hills Pool Home is the ONE You've Been Waiting For! Immaculately Maintained & Over 2400 S.F. Living Space and 3000+ S.F. Under Roof Boasts a Large Covered Pavered Lanai Overlooking the Sparkling Pool & Spa. Also a 3 C.G. with LOTS of Storage! The 1 Acre (mol) Lot is Fully Fenced in the Back for the Furry Ones! Interior Features SS & Granite Kitchen, Volume Coffered Ceilings, Wood & Ceramic Floors in Living Area, New Paint & Large Laundry Room w/Basin & Storage. Spacious Guest Bath Features a Dbl Vanity. Bali Blinds, Dual Pane Windows & Dual A/C System for Energy Efficiency! Also, No Mandatory Club Dues. Best Value in Citrus Hills! Call Today!
